I was responsible for data construction
and preprocessing, including implement-
ing download_data.py, prepare_splits.py,
parse_large_dict.py, and build_codemixed.py
to generate the synthetic Vietnamese–English
code-mixed dataset. I also implemented the
baseline model in baseline_lr.py. In the report,
he contributed to writing the Introduction, Dataset,
and parts of the Approach sections.

Both authors collaborated on model develop-
ment, experiment execution, and contributed to the
Related Work and Conclusion sections.